    "content": "<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">技能修改之</span>:<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">修罗邪光斩</span></span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在群里看到朋友琢磨了几天</span>,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还没修改出修罗邪光斩的攻击间隔</span></span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">于是就琢磨了一下</span></span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">先上图</span>,</span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"525\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/13/image-20230713213857-1.jpeg\" width=\"698\" /><img alt=\"\" height=\"524\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/13/image-20230713213857-2.jpeg\" width=\"700\" /><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方法</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用</span>PVF<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">工具打开 </span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">Script.pvf</span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然后找到</span>:</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">Skill -&gt; Swardman -&gt;</span></span></span>&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwave]: <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个是邪光斩 </span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">就是还没发育好的</span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwavecharge]: <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个就是修罗邪光斩了</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">需要蓄力后</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会变大的那个</span></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwaveex]: <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个就是修罗邪光斩的</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">ex, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学了这个技能</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">修罗邪光斩的技能威力变大</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">先修改</span>:</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwave]</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">找到</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[static data]</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">350</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[/static data]</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个</span> 350<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是攻击间隔</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">单位是毫秒</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">所以进游戏看就是</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">0.35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">秒了</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">.</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我修改的值是</span>: 11</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">11<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">比较好辨认，你随便修改也行</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然后修改</span>:</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwaveex]</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">找到</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[static data]</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">350</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[/static data]</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">350,<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">也修改成 </span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">11.</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最后修改</span>:</span></span></span>&nbsp;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwavecharge]</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">找到</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[static data]</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数值</span>1----&gt; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">代表蓄力需要多长时间</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越小值，需要蓄力的时间就越小</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">.</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数值</span>2----&gt; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">蓄力后的邪光斩的大小</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">越大越爽</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数值</span>3----&gt; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个是蓄力后的邪光斩的 长远，和速度</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数值</span>4----&gt; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这个是蓄力后的邪光斩的攻击间隔</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">单位是毫秒</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[/static data]</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">你可以按照我这样修改</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[grandwavecharge] <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">里面的</span></span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[static data]</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">10</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">320</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">350</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">10</span></span></span><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\">[/static data]</span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"93\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/13/image-20230713213857-3.jpeg\" width=\"530\" /><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5000pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">修改之后</span>, <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">记得覆盖到客户端的</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">服务端的其实可以不要替换</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如果你想替换也可以</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif\">.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">&nbsp;</p>",
